des: Tyler McDonough grounds into a force out, second baseman Mikey Perez to shortstop Danny De Andrade.   Chase Meidroth to 3rd.    Daniel Palka out at 2nd.    Tyler McDonough to 1st.
Tyler McDonough flies out to left fielder Connor Scott.
Tyler McDonough triples (2) on a fly ball to center fielder Colton Cowser.   Nick Decker scores.    Nick Sogard scores.
